---
title: Manhattan-Style Fish Chowder with Dill-Garlic Croutons
description: Savoury tomato broth and buttery barramundi make the perfect warming winter dinner, with crunchy dill-garlic croutons adding layers of taste and texture. This hearty soup is sure to become a weeknight go-to!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/manhattan-style-fish-chowder-f1bd0f1e.jpg
